#MIPS246 Assembler v1.0
***
[Download](https://raw.github.com/ceie246/MIPS/master/MIPS246/Release/MIPS246Assembler_1.0.rar)
* Assembler.CLI.exe - Assembler command line interface.
* Assembler.dll - Assembler core library. Can be used in the future porject.
* DataStructure.dll - Instruction c# model. Can be use in the future project.

I will upload the document of interface for the DLLs as soon as possible.

Any bugs please report [here](https://github.com/ceie246/MIPS/issues)!
